(Repeating) 
 THE RELIGIOUS RIGHT VS. McCAIN: IS IT ABOUT MONEY OR ABORTION?  
 (With CATHOLICS-POLITICS-REVIEW)  
 (The Week in Review)  
(bl) 
 By JILL ABRAMSON   
 c.2000 N.Y. Times News Service    
<TEXT>
<P>
   The bile between Sen. John McCain and the religious right
involves both God and Mammon.
</P>
<P>
   The Christian Coalition and the National Right to Life
Committee, which ran radio ads against McCain in New Hampshire and
