<P>
   ATLANTA _
</P>
<P>
   Nickelodeon's series ``Are You Afraid of the Dark?'' returns for
its seventh season on March 19. The kids of the Midnight Society
(at left) are back with more scary tales. In the first episode,
which has three parts, the kids become part of their tale. The show
airs at 6 p.m. each Sunday. _ Theresa Walsh Giarrusso
</P>
<P>
   HOOT AND GET HOMEWORK HELP
</P>
<P>
   If you're 7 to 12 years old, we have a cool place on the Web for
you to check out. It's www.cyberkids.com, and it has tons of stuff
for you to do. You can publish your creative works. You can hoot at
jokes and comic strips. You can learn a magic trick. You can read
movie, book and product reviews. And the site will hook you up with
homework help, too. _ Anne Y. Meyers
