   &UR; BRITAIN &LR;  &QC;  &LR;  &QL; 
 &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   &UR; PAMPERED BRITISH BUMS ARE FUSSY ABOUT TOILET TISSUE &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   Why does it cost more to wipe your bottom in Britain than in any
other country in the European Union? It is because British
consumers are extremely discriminating when it comes to toilet
paper. British bums, in short, demand and get the best. &QL;
</P>
<P>
   (375 words) &QL;
