impractical, a fact often overlooked amid the furor in Washington.
Beijing's vow to use force, made in a policy paper last month and
repeated in an editorial in a military newspaper today, is meant to
warn Taiwan away from formal independence and push it toward
serious negotiations on reunification with the mainland. A news
analysis by Craig S. Smith.
</P>
